file.string: Your username have been already taken, please try another username

Select a note and press the toggle button to hear it. The note played is displayed at the top-right hand corner. \nPress Adjust Octave to get back to Octave number 4. \nPress Adjust Note to get back to the note A of the current Octave.
"Hear the notes and then find them. The goal is to find the maximum of right notes."

At level 1, the game is waiting for you to play the right note. You need to scroll down or up the sheetmusic yourself. You can highlight the note yourself too.

At level 2, you have to play the note when it is highlight. If you play the good note at the right time you get one point.
At the end of the song, you can see how many notes you play right.

Levels 3 and 4 work the same way are level 2 but are harder.
